quran[29]{c,v,t}:
  91,1,"Nditsuba khuliuba nende obulafu bwalio!"
  91,2,"Nende khumwesi shingala kuliloondangakho!"
  91,3,"Nende khushitere olwa shiteranga!"
  91,4,"Nende khushiro olwa shifuumanga eshitere!"
  91,5,"Nende khulikulu nende ulia waliumbakha!"
  91,6,"Nende khuliloba nende ulia walikwalasia!"
  91,7,"Nende khu mwoyo nende ulia wakuleng’aasia!"
  91,8,"Mana nakumanyisia injila ya amabii nende ya amalayi."
  91,9,"Toto bwene yamala okhubura ulia wakutswenula."
  91,10,"Ne toto bwene yamala okhusikha ulia wakulekhula."
  91,11,"Babu Tsamudi bayingasia (omurumwa wabu) khulwa okhubeela obufuru bwabu."
  91,12,"Olwa yanguya ulia womwoyo omumu muno mubo."
  91,13,"Aho Omurumwa wa Nyasaye nababoolela mbu: "Ingamia ino ni ya Nyasaye, muyileshe inywe amatsi kayio ne mulayira tawe.""
  91,14,"Mana bamala bamukatsula, ne nibayisinza. Khulwako Nyasaye wabu Omulesi nabasishia khulwokhubeela tsimbi tsiabu nabamala boosi."
  91,15,"Naye sharitsanga akarulilaho tawe."
  92,1,"Nditsuba khu shilo olwashifunikhanga!"
  92,2,"Nende khushiteere olwa shiteeranga!"
  92,3,"Nende khuwaloonga eshisatsa nende eshikhasi!"
  92,4,"Toto bwene okhukhalabana khwenyu khwaukhane."
  92,5,"Kho, ulia urusia mana naaria Nyasaye,"
  92,6,"Mana naasubila muno kalia akali amalayi,"
  92,7,"Khwitsa okhumuwanguyisilia kabe amangu."
  92,8,"Ne ulia ukhola obwimani, mana niyelola mbu yeyerere."
  92,9,"Mana nakatsula amalayi po,"
  92,10,"Khwitsa okhumuwanguyisilia kabe amasiro!"
  92,11,"Ne omwandu kukwe kulimukhonya shina olwa aliba nasikhanga?"
  92,12,"Toto bwene kali khwifwe okhwechesia obulunjifu."
  92,13,"Ne toto bwene kali khwifwe ka mutsuli (akhera) nende kokhuranjilila."
  92,14,"Kho ebekanyisilie omulilo kwakhanga obutinyu!"